  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Explain a scenario where the magnetic and electric fields are crossed and their forces balance each other as a charged particle moves through a velocity selector</item>
<item>Compare how charge carriers move in a conductive material and explain how this relates to the Hall effect</item>
</list></md:abstract>
